<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>The studio · Huxley &amp; Co.</title>
<meta name="description" content="A two-principal talent practice held directly by Laura Huxley and Chad Siwik, based in Beverly Hills and London.">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Geist:wght@300;400;500;600&family=Geist+Mono:wght@400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
/* Huxley & Co. · site styles */

:root {
  --bg: #FAFAF7;
  --text: #0F0F0F;
  --text-muted: #4A4A4A;
  --meta: #6A6A6A;
  --meta-faint: #9A9A9A;
  --rule: rgba(15, 15, 15, 0.15);
  --rule-strong: #0F0F0F;
  --accent: #9C3520;

  --font-sans: 'Geist', 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
  --font-mono: 'Geist Mono', ui-monospace, 'SF Mono', Menlo, Consolas, monospace;

  --max-width: 1180px;
  --pad-x: 44px;
  --pad-y: 28px;
}

* { box-sizing: border-box; }

html, body {
  margin: 0;
  padding: 0;
  background: var(--bg);
  color: var(--text);
  font-family: var(--font-sans);
  font-size: 16px;
  line-height: 1.6;
  font-weight: 400;
  -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
  -moz-osx-font-smoothing: grayscale;
  text-rendering: optimizeLegibility;
}

a {
  color: inherit;
  text-decoration: none;
  transition: color 0.15s ease;
}

a:hover { color: var(--accent); }

.page {
  max-width: var(--max-width);
  margin: 0 auto;
  padding: var(--pad-y) var(--pad-x);
  min-height: 100vh;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
}

/* ---------- Document header ---------- */

.doc-header {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr auto;
  gap: 24px;
  padding-bottom: 14px;
  border-bottom: 0.5px solid var(--rule-strong);
  font-family: var(--font-mono);
  font-size: 10.5px;
  letter-spacing: 0.14em;
  color: var(--meta);
  text-transform: uppercase;
  align-items: baseline;
}

.doc-header .brand { color: var(--text); }

.doc-header nav {
  display: flex;
  gap: 28px;
}

.doc-header nav a {
  position: relative;
  padding-bottom: 2px;
}

.doc-header nav a.current { color: var(--text); }

.doc-header nav a.current::after {
  content: '';
  position: absolute;
  left: 0; right: 0; bottom: -3px;
  height: 0.5px;
  background: var(--accent);
}

/* ---------- Main column ---------- */

main {
  flex: 1;
  padding: 72px 0 56px;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
}

/* ---------- Section label with signet ---------- */

.section-label {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 14px;
  font-family: var(--font-mono);
  font-size: 10.5px;
  letter-spacing: 0.22em;
  color: var(--meta);
  text-transform: uppercase;
}

.signet {
  width: 22px;
  height: 22px;
  display: block;
  flex-shrink: 0;
  color: var(--text);
}

/* ---------- Hero headline ---------- */

h1.hero {
  font-family: var(--font-sans);
  font-size: clamp(36px, 5.5vw, 56px);
  line-height: 1.04;
  font-weight: 500;
  letter-spacing: -0.028em;
  margin: 36px 0 0;
  max-width: 18ch;
  color: var(--text);
}

/* ---------- Content prose ---------- */

.lede {
  margin-top: 40px;
  font-family: var(--font-sans);
  font-size: 20px;
  line-height: 1.55;
  color: var(--text);
  max-width: 44ch;
  font-weight: 400;
  letter-spacing: -0.006em;
}

.body {
  margin-top: 36px;
  max-width: 60ch;
}

.body p {
  font-size: 15.5px;
  line-height: 1.75;
  color: var(--text-muted);
  margin: 0 0 1.1em;
}

/* ---------- Numbered entries (services) ---------- */

.entries {
  margin-top: 64px;
  display: grid;
  gap: 44px;
}

.entry {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 80px 1fr;
  gap: 28px;
  padding-top: 20px;
  border-top: 0.5px solid var(--rule);
}

.entry-num {
  font-family: var(--font-mono);
  font-size: 10.5px;
  letter-spacing: 0.18em;
  color: var(--meta-faint);
  text-transform: uppercase;
  padding-top: 6px;
}

.entry-body h3 {
  font-family: var(--font-sans);
  font-size: 22px;
  font-weight: 500;
  letter-spacing: -0.014em;
  margin: 0 0 14px;
  color: var(--text);
}

.entry-body p {
  font-size: 15.5px;
  line-height: 1.75;
  color: var(--text-muted);
  margin: 0;
  max-width: 58ch;
}

/* ---------- Principals (studio page) ---------- */

.principals {
  margin-top: 56px;
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
  gap: 48px;
}

.principal {
  padding-top: 20px;
  border-top: 0.5px solid var(--rule);
}

.principal .label {
  font-family: var(--font-mono);
  font-size: 10.5px;
  letter-spacing: 0.2em;
  color: var(--meta-faint);
  text-transform: uppercase;
  margin-bottom: 18px;
}

.principal h3 {
  font-family: var(--font-sans);
  font-size: 22px;
  font-weight: 500;
  letter-spacing: -0.014em;
  margin: 0 0 6px;
}

.principal .role {
  font-family: var(--font-mono);
  font-size: 10.5px;
  letter-spacing: 0.18em;
  color: var(--meta);
  text-transform: uppercase;
  margin-bottom: 18px;
}

.principal p {
  font-size: 15px;
  line-height: 1.72;
  color: var(--text-muted);
  margin: 0;
}

/* ---------- Enquire form ---------- */

.enquire {
  margin-top: 56px;
  max-width: 52ch;
}

.field {
  display: block;
  margin-bottom: 28px;
}

.field label {
  display: block;
  font-family: var(--font-mono);
  font-size: 10px;
  letter-spacing: 0.22em;
  color: var(--meta);
  text-transform: uppercase;
  margin-bottom: 8px;
}

.field input,
.field textarea {
  display: block;
  width: 100%;
  font-family: var(--font-sans);
  font-size: 15.5px;
  line-height: 1.6;
  color: var(--text);
  background: transparent;
  border: none;
  border-bottom: 0.5px solid var(--rule-strong);
  padding: 6px 0 10px;
  outline: none;
  border-radius: 0;
  transition: border-color 0.15s ease;
}

.field input:focus,
.field textarea:focus {
  border-bottom-color: var(--accent);
}

.field textarea {
  resize: vertical;
  min-height: 110px;
}

.submit {
  display: inline-block;
  background: transparent;
  border: none;
  font-family: var(--font-mono);
  font-size: 11px;
  letter-spacing: 0.2em;
  color: var(--text);
  text-transform: uppercase;
  padding: 10px 0;
  cursor: pointer;
  border-bottom: 0.5px solid var(--text);
  transition: color 0.15s ease, border-color 0.15s ease;
  margin-top: 4px;
}

.submit:hover {
  color: var(--accent);
  border-bottom-color: var(--accent);
}

.direct-contact {
  margin-top: 48px;
  padding-top: 20px;
  border-top: 0.5px solid var(--rule);
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 110px 1fr;
  gap: 18px 28px;
  max-width: 56ch;
}

.direct-contact .dc-label {
  font-family: var(--font-mono);
  font-size: 10.5px;
  letter-spacing: 0.22em;
  color: var(--meta);
  text-transform: uppercase;
  padding-top: 3px;
}

.direct-contact .dc-value {
  font-family: var(--font-sans);
  font-size: 14.5px;
  color: var(--text);
  line-height: 1.55;
}

.direct-contact .dc-value a { color: var(--text); }
.direct-contact .dc-value a:hover { color: var(--accent); }

/* ---------- Document footer ---------- */

.doc-footer {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr auto 1fr;
  gap: 24px;
  padding-top: 14px;
  border-top: 0.5px solid var(--rule-strong);
  font-family: var(--font-mono);
  font-size: 10.5px;
  letter-spacing: 0.14em;
  color: var(--meta);
  text-transform: uppercase;
  align-items: baseline;
}

.doc-footer .center { text-align: center; }
.doc-footer .cta { text-align: right; color: var(--accent); }

/* ---------- Page-load reveal ---------- */

@media (prefers-reduced-motion: no-preference) {
  .reveal > * {
    opacity: 0;
    transform: translateY(6px);
    animation: reveal 0.7s cubic-bezier(0.2, 0.6, 0.2, 1) forwards;
  }
  .reveal > *:nth-child(1) { animation-delay: 0.05s; }
  .reveal > *:nth-child(2) { animation-delay: 0.18s; }
  .reveal > *:nth-child(3) { animation-delay: 0.34s; }
  .reveal > *:nth-child(4) { animation-delay: 0.52s; }
  .reveal > *:nth-child(5) { animation-delay: 0.72s; }

  @keyframes reveal {
    to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
  }
}

/* ---------- Responsive ---------- */

@media (max-width: 820px) {
  :root {
    --pad-x: 24px;
    --pad-y: 22px;
  }
  .doc-header,
  .doc-footer {
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 10px;
  }
  .doc-header nav {
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 18px;
  }
  .doc-footer .cta { text-align: left; }
  .doc-footer .center { text-align: left; }
  h1.hero { font-size: clamp(30px, 9vw, 42px); max-width: none; }
  main { padding: 48px 0 36px; }
  .entry { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 10px; }
  .principals { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 36px; }
  .lede { font-size: 18px; }
}

/* ---------- Print ---------- */

@media print {
  body { background: #fff; }
  .doc-header, .doc-footer { border-color: #000; }
  .reveal > * { opacity: 1; transform: none; animation: none; }
}

</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="page">

  <header class="doc-header">
    <span class="brand">Huxley &amp; Co. &nbsp;·&nbsp; Independent talent practice</span>
    <nav aria-label="Primary">
      <a href="work.html">The work</a>
      <a href="studio.html" class="current">The studio</a>
      <a href="inquire.html">Inquire</a>
    </nav>
  </header>

  <main class="reveal">
    <div class="section-label">
      <svg class="signet" width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 22 22" aria-hidden="true">
        <rect x="0.75" y="0.75" width="20.5" height="20.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="0.5"/>
        <line x1="7.5" y1="5.5" x2="7.5" y2="16.5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="0.8"/>
        <line x1="14.5" y1="5.5" x2="14.5" y2="16.5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="0.8"/>
        <line x1="7.5" y1="11" x2="14.5" y2="11" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="0.8"/>
      </svg>
      <span>№ 003 &nbsp;·&nbsp; The studio</span>
    </div>

    <p class="lede">A founder-led practice with an international client base. We take a small number of mandates each year and hold every engagement directly.</p>

    <div class="body">
      <p>Huxley &amp; Co. exists in the space between traditional executive search and in-house talent leadership. Most of what we do is invisible from the outside: a confidential brief, a quiet longlist, a set of conversations, a placement. We prefer it that way, and so do our clients.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="principals">

      <article class="principal">
        <div class="label">Principal</div>
        <h3>Laura Huxley</h3>
        <div class="role">Founder</div>
        <p>Laura began her career in London across PR, television, arts, and live events, before moving into talent advisory in Los Angeles and Europe. She went on to embed with one of the world's leading multidisciplinary creative studios, placing the people behind some of its largest global productions. At Huxley &amp; Co. she works with principals and founders across design, sport, and hospitality who hold themselves to an uncommon standard. Understanding people, she believes, is the only honest basis for placing them.</p>
      </article>

      <article class="principal">
        <div class="label">Advisor</div>
        <h3>Chad Siwik</h3>
        <div class="role">Strategy</div>
        <p>Chad is an advisor to Huxley &amp; Co., where he contributes on strategy and select search mandates. He is concurrently at NASA, working on communications and strategy across the Artemis missions. Operating inside one of the most security-conscious institutions in the world has given him a rare fluency in discretion, precision, and the kind of trust earned only over time. He brings that standard to every engagement at Huxley &amp; Co.</p>
      </article>

    </div>
  </main>

  <footer class="doc-footer">
    <span>thehuxleycompany.com</span>
    <span class="center">LA &nbsp;·&nbsp; London &nbsp;·&nbsp; MMXXVI</span>
    <a class="cta" href="inquire.html">↘ Inquire</a>
  </footer>

</div>
</body>
</html>
